</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[299,329,909,934]" captionStart="FIGURES 56 – 62" captionStartId="11.[151,264,1346,1368]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,267,1324]" captionTargetId="figure@11.[151,1436,267,1324]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="FIGURES 56 – 62. Male genitalia of species of Argyrogrammana collected at the PNSD. 56. A. praestigiosa. 57. A. johannismarci. 58. A. brevignoni sp. nov. holotype. 59. A. rameli. 60. A. willmotti sp. nov. holotype. 61. A. iracyi. 62. A. saulensis tunari comb. nov. Left to right: dorsal view of uncus, lateral view of tegumen, saccus, uncus, gnathos, valva and aedeagus, and ventral view of valva. Scale bar = 1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/233293/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="243">61</figureCitation>
