<figureCitation box="[341,370,909,934]" captionStart="FIGURES 63 – 66" captionStartId="15.[151,264,1830,1852]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,253,1808]" captionTargetId="figure@15.[151,1436,253,1809]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURES 63 – 66. Female genitalia of species of Argyrogrammana collected at the PNSD. 63. A. gallardi sp. nov. (tentatively determination). 64. A. willmotti, sp. nov. allotype. 65. A. iracyi. 66. A. saulensis tunari comb. nov. Top to bottom lateral view of papila analis and ventral view of sterigma and bursae copulatrix. Scale bar = 1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/233294/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="243">
